  ENTitle: Shard Refinement II
  ENDesc: Allows you to upgrade Item Fragments up to Level 2 using Enhancement Stones.
  FRTitle: Raffinage des Fragments II
  FRDesc: "Permet d\u2019am\xE9liorer les Fragments d\u2019objet jusqu\u2019au niveau
    2 \xE0 l\u2019aide de Pierres d\u2019am\xE9lioration."
